io.k8s.api.apidiscovery.v2beta1.APIGroup.description: APIGroupDiscoveryList is a resource containing a list of APIGroupDiscovery. This is one of the types able to be returned from the /api and /apis endpoint and contains an aggregated list of API resources (built-ins, Custom Resource Definitions, resources from aggregated servers) that a cluster supports.

APIGroupDiscovery holds information about which resources are being served for all version of the API Group. It contains a list of APIVersionDiscovery that holds a list of APIResourceDiscovery types served for a version. Versions are in descending order of preference, with the first version being the preferred entry.

io.k8s.api.apidiscovery.v2beta1.APIVersi.description: APIVersionDiscovery holds a list of APIResourceDiscovery types that are served for a particular version within an API Group.

version.description: version is the name of the version within a group version.

freshness.description: freshness marks whether a group version's discovery document is up to date.

io.k8s.api.apidiscovery.v2beta1.APIResou.description: APIResourceDiscovery provides information about an API resource for discovery.

resource.description: resource is the plural name of the resource.

scope.description: scope indicates the scope of a resource, either Cluster or Namespaced

singularResource.description: singularResource is the singular name of the resource.

verbs.description: verbs is a list of supported API operation types

shortNames.description: shortNames is a list of suggested short names of the resource.

categories.description: categories is a list of the grouped resources this resource belongs to.

io.k8s.api.apidiscovery.v2beta1.APISubre.description: APISubresourceDiscovery provides information about an API subresource for discovery.

subresource.description: subresource is the name of the subresource.

verbs.description: verbs is a list of supported API operation types
